1 = First-Step --> nodemone, mongodb, mongoose, express, dotenv, crose --> aguli project install kore nite hobe.

*** nodemone install korar karone package.json file debug section "start": "nodemone index.js" likhe nite hobe then npm start korte hobe.

2 = Database Create kore nite hobe and database link .env file rakhte hobe then database folder kore tar majhe db.js file Create kore (const mongoose = require('mongoose')) set kore akti function likhe mongoose theke database connection code nite hobe then function er vhitore code rakhe (process.env.MONGODBURL) .env file theke url access korte hobe

last kaj index.js file databse require kore nite hobe, then dotenv, cros

